{"tid":1806032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元旦大遊行和理非手足必加技能","createTime":"2020-01-01T04:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T06:40:53.000Z","uid":258118,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"29d64114b800b37e30b8d2c954bc2fd2b5396f3e","tid":1806032,"uid":258118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"2020年新開始! New year new you! <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">係時候升lv啦! </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊行巴絲今日可以主力加 兩大<strong>和理非</strong>技能點:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 大叫口號</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n成日遊行都見到人只行唔叫，其實都出到黎，又遮住曬塊面，唔洗怕羞，有<strong>咁大聲得咁大聲</strong>。 平時你唔會打狗，起碼比d勇氣叫，幫前線手足打氣。 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有，令我地泉下既手足都聽到，我地要幫佢地行落去，仲要叫落去</span>，我相信佢地如果仲在生應該會用盡全力叫。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 行足全程</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有人中途加入 (前線另計)，有人行到見到地鐵站就走，喂大佬，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>出黎遊行最最最基本就係</strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"> &quot;行&quot;</span></strong></span>， 係行哂呀大佬，行都要偷雞點對得住死去既兄弟呀?! <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一陣維園見啦!<br />\n香港人 加油，反抗，報仇!</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e8ea43a7846947f2e6384a5e9f6aa5acd22b0244","tid":1806032,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADV9aSP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADV9aSP.png&h=291c3a32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcb7ab15e2b0d8ddf1028e61b699accb98833d0c","tid":1806032,"uid":131040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"一陣維園見"},{"pid":"b800e0a9413b8c222eb6a753520b4ae98de